en_116621_1	Diyasenpura Wimala Thero, the resident monk at ‘Bavunseth Mind Relaxing Meditation Center’ at Helummahara, Dekatana trained one more Officer and fifty-six Other Ranks of the Sri Lanka Army for meditation on Friday (8) at the invitation of the Directorate of Psychological Operations at the Army Headquarters.
en_116621_2	This is an ongoing project, meant to raise mental relaxation and tranquility in mind.
